longBusinessSummary: Cello World Limited manufactures and sells consumer houseware and glassware products in India and internationally. The company offers drinkware products, including bottles, flasks, jugs, tea sets, coffee mugs, and tumblers; lunch boxes and carriers; storage items such as water jugs, chillers, and ice pails; dinnerware products, such as dinner sets, minimalistic melamine dinner sets, casseroles, trays, and serve wares; bakeware and gift sets; and kitchen appliances. It also provides cookware series and cleaning aids for homes, comprising brushes, wipers, brooms, mops, sponge wipes, cloths, dustbins, and bathroom accessories, such as bathroom sets, buckets, tubs, basins, dry fruit sets, laundry baskets, stools, plates, mugs, and soap cases. In addition, the company offers health products, including UV sanitizers, air purifiers, and fruit and vegetable washers; household appliances; and furniture products, such as chairs, dining tables, desks, stools, storage units, shelves, racks, and cabinets. The company also sells its products online. Founded in 1958, Cello World Limited is headquartered in Goregaon, India.
